ActFarm Income Protection Act
PrecisAuthorisation to provide for federal contributions of up to $13,860,000 to assist MANITOBA PRODUCERS, affected by late-season flooding in 2008, to re-establish forage crops, forage seed fields and pasture and to assist the producers with direct feed costs.
